8:["$","$1","c",{"children":[["$","main",null,{"className":"pt-24","children":[["$","section",null,{"className":"section","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"container-x grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-2","children":[["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"eyebrow mb-5","children":"About Sou Sik"}],["$","h1",null,{"className":"text-4xl md:text-6xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-balance","children":"從產品開發開始，而不是從行銷開始。"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose-sou","children":[["$","p",null,{"children":"Sou Sik 是一個以精密機械與精品咖啡為核心的磨豆機品牌。我們先把時間花在產品結構、研磨手感與長期使用體驗上，然後才回頭建立這個官網。"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"因為我們相信，品牌不是包裝出來的，而是從每一次使用者轉動手柄、感受到阻力變化、聽見齒輪聲音的那一刻開始成立。"}]]}]]}]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"section bg-white/[.03]","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"container-x grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-3","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"card","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"mb-3 text-2xl font-semibold","children":"Mechanical"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-7 text-white/60","children":"讓機械結構成為體驗本身，而不是被隱藏的零件。"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"card","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"mb-3 text-2xl font-semibold","children":"Coffee"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-7 text-white/60","children":"服務真實沖煮，不只服務規格表。從淺焙到日常出杯，都要更穩定。"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"card","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"mb-3 text-2xl font-semibold","children":"Ritual"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-7 text-white/60","children":"研磨不是準備動作，它是咖啡體驗的第一段儀式。"}]]}]]}]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"section","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"container-x max-w-4xl prose-sou","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"我們想改變什麼？"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"很多手搖磨豆機把「硬、費力、卡頓」視為理所當然，尤其面對淺焙豆時更明顯。Sou Sik 想做的是，把機械工程導入咖啡工具，讓省力、穩定與可玩性同時存在。"}],["$","h2",null,{"children":"第一款產品 P-1"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"P-1 是 Sou Sik 的第一個正式回答。它使用行星齒輪減力系統，搭配大尺寸錐刀與低殘粉設計，讓手搖磨豆機不再只是功能工具，而是可以被欣賞、被拆解、被理解的機械器物。"}]]}]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"secti